text: Gustave Cabaret was an archer from France. He was born on 1 November 1866 and died on 4 April 1918. Cabaret competed at the 1908 Summer Olympics.Gustave CabaretGustave CABARET == References == Category:1866 births Category:1918 deaths Category:French archers Category:Olympians for France
